---
title: Double-Smoked Bacon Penne in a Tomato Arrabbiata Sauce
description: Translating to “angry” in Italian, arrabbiata is known for its fiery kick. We’ve reinvented this Italian classic by adding salty bacon to the mix. Wilting spinach into the sauce is a great way to sneak in extra greens. If you’re not a fan of heat, simply tone down (or leave out) the chili pepper!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/59e8b756450cfa09d86d5ef2-72d8a368.jpg
